Magic ingredients
Hys asks you to bring him some ingredients from his lab that he needs for his spells. It is possible that after this he will agree to help.
#subobj 1
Go to the lab
This time there should be no problems with the lab - the traps are off and the guardian tigers are gone.
#subobj 2
Destroy the 'tail'
Unknown people have organized a ruse, you need to get away from them.
#subobj 3
Get the ingredients
Everything you need lies in a box next to the lab.